cost/utilization: a measure of system performance.wa method is presented for evaluating computersystem performance in terms of a cost/utilization factor and a measure of imbalance.  these coefficientsindicate the extent to which the total system cost is effectively utilized.  the method includes atechnique for the visual representation of system performance.cacm march, borovits, i.ein-dor, p..kcomputer system, performance evaluation, cost/utilization, system balance.c.ca jb december ,   : am